    "_postman_id": "ikibisnis-role-collection-v1",
    "name": "IkiBisnis — Role Management API",
    "description": "Koleksi lengkap endpoint Role Management API.\n\n**Base URL:** `{{base_url}}/api/v1/roles`\n\n**Cara pakai:**\n1. Set variable `base_url` → `http://localhost:3001`\n2. Jalankan **Create Role** dulu, lalu copy `id` dari response ke variable `role_id`\n3. Semua endpoint lain sudah otomatis menggunakan `{{role_id}}`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:3001",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Base URL aplikasi"
    },
    {
      "key": "role_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "UUID role — otomatis terisi setelah Create Role dijalankan"
    }
  ],
